data.description: **Open House Saturday February 10th 12:30-3:00pm** Nestled within the secure embrace of Worthom Oaks, this 4-bedroom, 3-bath haven welcomes you with a sense of tranquility. Boasting a brand-new roof, the home stands as a testament to modern comfort and style. Step into the updated master bathroom, where a luxurious rainfall shower awaits, accompanied by contemporary lighting that casts a warm glow.  The heart of this residence lies in its spacious living areas, providing ample room for family gatherings. As you step outside, an oversized deck beckons, promising an ideal setting for outdoor celebrations and relaxation under the open sky.  Worthom Oaks offers not one but two neighborhood swimming pools, inviting residents to enjoy leisurely swims on sunny days. The community takes pride in its commitment to education, with an elementary school within walking distance and plans for a new middle school on the horizon.  Discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and community in this idyllic home within the gated community of Worthom Oaks.
